data.description: Welcome to an exquisite 2 bed, 2 bath home with a den, located in the highly sought-after Sun River 55+ active community. This tastefully upgraded residence offers a blend of comfort and style within its open floor plan.  As you enter, embrace the inviting warmth and cozy atmosphere of this delightful living space. Experience a touch of sophistication with the plantation shutters, giving you the flexibility to customize the natural light streaming into the room. The kitchen boasts updated appliances and a thoughtfully designed layout that seamlessly blends functionality with aesthetics.  Outside, your own backyard oasis awaits, where you can fire up the grill and bask in the breathtaking views of the southern skis and the meticulously landscaped surroundings. This home is not just a residence; it's a gateway to an exceptional lifestyle within an active adult community. Residents can indulge in a variety of amenities, including golf, pickle ball, a refreshing pool, workout facilities, and a rich array of craft classes and events.  Experience the perfect blend of convenience and an active lifestyle in this remarkable home. Embrace the serenity of a well-appointed home paired with the vibrancy of a community that caters to your every need. Welcome to a life of comfort, elegance, and endless possibilities in Sun River. Sun Valley offers on-site chef, tennis and pickle ball court, Pool, spa, poolside cafe, dog park, onsite personal trainer, wood shop, pottery shop and classes.
